<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Scenic Acres</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">
                A warm and welcoming neighborhood in the NW Calgary area, Scenic Acres homes boast of some of the most incredible panoramic views in the city and offers its residents a beautiful landscape to gaze upon. Apart from the breathtaking mountain views of the Rockies, the community also offers an enchanting birdâ€™s eye view of the nearby Paskapoo Slopes as well.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">The community in Scenic Acres totally lives up to its name and offers some of the most picturesque locations for settling down in your dream home.</p>
            <p class="par-lg"> Living in this tranquil paradise is an experience that never lets you feel isolated from the world out there, courtesy the well connected LRT and bus services that will take you wherever you want to go.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">
                The community in Scenic Acres has over the last couple of decades played host to rapidly growing population, predominantly consisting of young families, seeking a great place to raise their children; while still being able to enjoy living and working in a large city. The Scenic Acres Real Estate market is quite well developed with inventory predominantly favoring detached 3-4 bedroom single family homes with average prices in the mid $600,000 range, though some older but still well maintained homes for sale in Scenic Acres at extremely attractive rates.
            </p>
        </div>
